raw.subject:
ARM PrimeCell Synchronous Serial Port (PL022)
Technical Reference Manual. This book provides reference documentation
for System-on-Chip (SoC) engineers who want to integrate the ARM
PrimeCell SSP peripheral into a system. It describes functional
blocks, registers, programming details, and signals.
